sequenceDiagram
    participant CF as Configurator/Scheduler
    participant API as API Gateway
    participant CJM as Cleansing Job Manager
    participant CE as Cleansing Engine
    participant ST as Cleansed Storage
    participant MD as Metadata Registry
    participant NT as Notification Service

    CF->>API: POST /cleansing-jobs (tenant, dataset, rule version)
    API->>CJM: Create cleansing job plan
    CJM->>MD: Record job submission + parameters
    CJM->>CE: Dispatch transformation plan
    CE->>CE: Apply ordered transformations
    CE->>ST: Persist cleansed dataset + rejection set
    CE->>MD: Emit before/after metrics + rejection reasons
    CE->>CJM: Return completion status
    CJM->>NT: Trigger completion/alert notification
    NT->>CF: Deliver success/failure update
    CF->>API: Retrieve cleansing report or download cleansed data
